            <div class="field-item odd">
                      <div class="field-label-inline-first">
              Librarian Comment:&nbsp;</div>
                    <p>This is an eight volume series about Queen Potema, the Wolf Queen of  Solitude.&nbsp;There is a scribe's errors in this series. The most  notable is the mention of the Psijic Master Iachesis. This name was  mistakenly translated and should be &quot;Celarus&quot; instead. Further more some typesetting errors. The first is in the book five,   it's on this part &quot;...all the known lands beyond, Atmora, Yokunda,   Akavir, Pyandonea...&quot;. The second known land should be &quot;Yokuda&quot; not   &quot;Yokunda&quot;. The second typo is on the last book. &quot;He marries Katarish,   Duchess of Vvardenfell.&quot; The Duchess of Vvardenfell is &quot;Katariah&quot; not   &quot;Katarish&quot;.</p>
        </div>
